Device-Opto22 version 0.01
==========================

WHAT IS THIS?

A simple module to communicate and control Opto22 Brains via a Memory Mapped Protocol.
Opto22 makes a complete line of industrial IO modules.  

HOW DO I INSTALL IT?

To install this module, cd to the directory that contains this README
file and type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

WHAT SYSTEMS DOES IT WORK WITH?

This module has been used on Linux servers on INTEL/AMD servers. May work 
under Windows or other O/S but I have not tested on these. 

WHERE ARE THE EXAMPLES?

I have source code available for samples. If you need this contact me. 
http://perlworks.com

